    "| `province` | Do **not** drop rows | Missingness is too common and non-harmful |\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "### 3.8 Final Preprocessing Decisions for Missing Values\n",
    "\n",
    "The missing-value policy should be **feature-specific**, not global.\n",
